# No client-side secrets required.
# Firebase config is committed in firebase-applet-config.json (public API keys, protected by Firestore rules).
# If you need server-side secrets (e.g., for Cloud Functions), put them in .env.local (gitignored).

# Example:
# SENDGRID_API_KEY=...
# GEMINI_API_KEY=...  # only on server-side (Functions)
